<subSubSection id="9EA2B0F7777AC32456CA4AB052D3DA23" pageId="2" pageNumber="223" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="D607E37C777AC32456CA4AB052D3DA23" blockId="2.[707,1193,194,507]" pageId="2" pageNumber="223">
<emphasis id="E4CC3F6E777AC32456CA4AB05521DBF8" bold="true" box="[731,851,194,215]" pageId="2" pageNumber="223">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named in honor of the noted coleopterist and collector of the unique 
<typeStatus id="09035DDE777AC32450204AAF52F1DBDD" box="[1073,1155,221,242]" pageId="2" pageNumber="223">holotype</typeStatus>
